JULIE Sentence Boundary Detector (JSBD)

Introduction
============
JSBD is a ML-based sentence splitter. It can be retrained on supported
training material and is thus neither language nor domain dependent.



Dependencies
============ 
JSBD is based on the machine learning toolkit MALLET (Version 0.4). The
necessary libraries are included in the lib/ directory.


Usage
=====

To run JSBD just type "java -jar JSBD-1.x.jar". This will show the available modes.

Documentation
==============
For further information please refer to the documentation, JSBD-1.x.pdf.


